text:
[Verse]
Sunshine in your eyes
Morning light goodbye
Glistening skies so high
You and I just fly

[Verse 2]
Skipping stones on the lake
Memories we make
Every smile not fake
Hearts that never break

[Chorus]
Oh-oh we're alive
Dancing through the night
Never want to hide
Feeling so light inside

[Verse 3]
Trails of golden dreams
Water flowing streams
Laughter's all it seems
Love's bursting at the seams

[Chorus]
Oh-oh we're alive
Dancing through the night
Never want to hide
Feeling so light inside

[Bridge]
Echoes in the breeze
Whispering so free
Life's a melody
Together you and me
title: Sunshine Eyes
